<section style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48EU5rGMLmwIGd9shzpC7Vib9zoAIcm9LblZmMf4jrj1q6ns2EuGzRxTXQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="1.3263157894736841" data-w="380"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">Hello~周六夜剧场又和大家见面了！这次给大家带来一部正在更新的美剧《Quarry》（亡命之徒，第一季），很适合现在想开新剧的朋友们。而且，我保证坑很深，不出到个什么三、四季的，我就……算了，不要立flag，还记得上次推荐的Helix吗，不就第二季夭折了……</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">总之只是想表达这部Cinemax新出的美剧，确实很有潜力。那么下面我会尽量讲讲，到底这部剧为什么评价如此之高。然后例行的推荐歌曲，就给大家强推一首最近洗脑的歌吧，也比较适合这部剧的风格：来自Echosmith的Cool Kids，不插电版。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><qqmusic class="res_iframe qqmusic_iframe js_editor_qqmusic" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" musicid="5924077" mid="002oSsnr0YhW1z" albumurl="/C/I/003VO0tE1Z8iCI.jpg" audiourl="http://ws.stream.qqmusic.qq.com/C100002oSsnr0YhW1z.m4a?fromtag=46" music_name="Cool&nbsp;Kids" commentid="1845485907" singer="Echosmith&nbsp;-&nbsp;Acoustic&nbsp;Dreams" play_length="236000" src="/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/qqmusic_tmpl&amp;singer=Echosmith%20-%20Acoustic%20Dreams&amp;music_name=Cool%20Kids"></qqmusic></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">点开播放键之后，让我们回到美剧。IMDb评分8.3，虽然比不上最近被炒得火热的《西部世界》，但分也绝不算低。而且，70年代越战归来的背景，确实在画面上拉低了这部剧的评分，但这并不影响剧组的布景，和在每个细节上的设置，这也是Quarry这部剧广受好评的原因之一。画面的内容虽然是简陋的，但却做得很精致，尤其多次利用第一视角，让人有身临其境的感觉。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48EP6a4Hqlz5RuMk4O2GYJV4lHZrVibJ3q2ociaUyzEMBibcYc05U4GvYvkw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;">（请原谅我截图的像素渣）</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">Quarry一词本意为采石场，美剧中这样定义这个词（中文是我自己翻译的）：</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</span></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(247, 242, 236);"><section class="" style="border-left-color: rgb(84, 37, 92); border-right-color: rgb(84, 37, 92); border-left-style: dotted; border-left-width: 6px; border-right-style: dotted; border-right-width: 6px; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">Hollowed out on the inside, hard as rock.</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;">外表醉翁无意，内心坚若磐石。</strong></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48E7micLiagkFR9Wm0NmBl7mNsfp3KURS2gZicy1MzRbNpicEfZaksTdvOIPQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">在某些地方，这部剧很像《碟中谍》，人物利益关系错综复杂，一圈套一圈，挣脱了一环，就有可能被另一环压死。主人公就像是一枚棋子，他当然不甘于此，想要挣脱被摆布的局势，至于木偶如何挣脱提线，请看Quarry第一季！</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48ElkONCbucKK4ueXh3Md3yQbSbbGpakziaH5tCtBUXk94ISTxz77SzXJw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">另一点一定要提的是男主，堪称整部剧的演技担当。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">男主Logan Marshall-Green，未来将出演《蜘蛛侠》，在这部美剧里他演技超神，可以毫不夸张地说是美剧届里的演技担当之一了。由于美剧更多地聚焦男主，所以其心理表现就要在每一处细微的动作、表情中演绎出来，这不是一张截图能说明的事情，但还是附上一张图感受一下。</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48Ek2azEqiak9d74BGVBkx4FHm0O1ZicE1wL24hNFibkAoCDxSghMCeeCArA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5625" data-w="640"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box;">和自己一个战壕里爬出来的好友，在自己面前死掉而自己却无能为力，身体的抽动演绎得很真实自然，这些吧，还是大家看了才知道。这种真实的细节累积，让人越发地爱上这位男主。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">总的来说，这一部以情节、态度和演技取胜的美剧。看着老前辈们，如《神盾局特工》、《绿箭侠》都更到了第四季，《亡命之徒》可以说代表了美剧界的新生力量。导演们并不一定要把预算都投在那些宏大的场面上，反而把每一处细节做好，也是给观众一种别致的体验。这就是Quarry，亡命之徒。</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style=" text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;  box-sizing: border-box; "><img style="vertical-align: middle; box-sizing: border-box;" src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lZxqO3dCoYjNnU6UJ6mWMVRJdDQel48ELsqJW6UmHoe2z4fYWPYpTqcZgQyrhluyPxQVmMDvnECiage7f8GM0LQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-w="600"  /></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">外表醉翁无意，内心坚若磐石。说的就是美国这种70年代的忧伤吧，没什么是值得自己去守护的了，但却还坚挺在这个世界上。</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="   box-sizing: border-box; " powered-by="xiumi.us"><section class="" style="   box-sizing: border-box; "><section class="" style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"  /></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">以上就是本次周六夜剧场的全部内容了，由于下周工大就要开模联会啦，所以请允许我偷懒少写一些咯XD 晚安好梦~</p></section></section></section><section class="Powered-by-XIUMI V5" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section class="" style="text-align: center; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: right; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word !important;">付晓玲 渠海港&nbsp;| 审核</span></p><p style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(84, 37, 92); font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; text-align: right; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 